Tanasha Donna has announced that she is set to release her debut album next year. The singer has risen to fame through songs like 'La Vie', 'Sawa' and her collabo with ex Diamond, 'Gere'. Announcing the news to her fans, she wrote, "2020 has been a year of hits on hits. 7 hits in less than a year, and it's not me, it's all because of the love and support you continued to show me. "...Alhamdulillah. 2021, Let's make history. East Africa to the World." Early this year, Tanasha released her debut EP, 'The Donna Tella EP'. Apart from music, Tanasha is a model and a mother of one son. She was featured by Ali Kiba in his song 'Nagharamia'.